{"tid":666725,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"19座小巴超載至25人　警打擊行動拘3司機","createTime":"2018-05-16T06:27:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-16T10:50:43.000Z","uid":153228,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"454677a90187132bd44cf720a992f71d15f3d77d","tid":666725,"uid":153228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T06:27:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180516/s00001/1526439999816\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180516%2Fs00001%2F1526439999816&d=71H6aUdLW1dRq8EZX0xA2TANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=e926ab8c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180516%2Fs00001%2F1526439999816&h=9b861a8a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180516/s00001/1526439999816</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180516/s00001/05036fcb0303905e3a26a6237a3993d1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180516%2Fs00001%2F05036fcb0303905e3a26a6237a3993d1.jpg&h=ae34cbc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n71歲女司機被警方問話。（蔡方山攝）<br />\n<br />\n警方今晨在元朗進行打擊小巴超載行動，拘捕3名年齡51至71歲的小巴司機，行動中發現3部紅頂小巴超載，其中一部19座小巴超載6人。<br />\n<br />\n新界北交通特遣隊今晨部署行動，出動便衣探員及隱形戰車調查。行動中截獲3部來往元朗至大棠的小巴，懷疑超載。其中一部19座新型小巴超載6人，共接載25人，其中部分乘客站立，部分則坐在車頭的木箱。<br />\n<br />\n另外兩部小巴均為舊式16座位小巴，分別超載兩名及三名乘客。警方以危險駕駛罪名拘捕兩男一女司機，其中71歲女司機駕駛19座小巴，三部小巴正被扣查，檢查是否有其他違規改裝。<br />\n<br />\n新界北交通特遣隊署理警署警長黃國遠指，來往元朗及大棠路線以清晨5至6時超載時間最嚴重，因當時未有其他交通工具，部分市民趕上早班，在車少人多情況下，部分司機鋌而走險。<br />\n<br />\n黃指，已記錄超載小巴上乘客的個人資料，稍後會聯絡部分乘客落口供，是否票控則視乎調查結果。黃又呼籲市民不要乘坐超載小巴，一旦發生意外會很危險。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180516/s00001/05076493e8a1ccec8a3dfa9ba9925be0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180516%2Fs00001%2F05076493e8a1ccec8a3dfa9ba9925be0.jpg&h=86b69d27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n十九座小巴上加裝木箱，相信供超載乘客乘坐。（蔡方山攝）"},{"pid":"18d6d107bc0181f1b99db1d068effb3d5027c595","tid":666725,"uid":22291,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T06:31:19.000Z","msg":"屌 連返工個陣都要比狗玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88118541e3c5b68e9b48c1fcac033ee2524dca19","tid":666725,"uid":73915,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T06:33:21.000Z","msg":"企位<br />\n痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bf0d5d3207a48b90bd40d011bb74669acc33829","tid":666725,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T06:35:02.000Z","msg":"點坐呀"},{"pid":"8e8c3e58ed5167b57f3880be0b85b896e4327bca","tid":666725,"uid":52605,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T06:40:44.000Z","msg":"港豬為咗返工 小巴都肯企"},{"pid":"3b9ffbdfe6a3bfc8f0deb0e98dc61ba96db2302f","tid":666725,"uid":51532,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T06:45:35.000Z","msg":"7張野都可以揸車？"},{"pid":"9672dfcbabe461adf0d909ebb53713f8aeac8fc5","tid":666725,"uid":160662,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3b9ffbdfe6a3bfc8f0deb0e98dc61ba96db2302f","tid":666725,"uid":51532,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T06:45:35.000Z","msg":"7張野都可以揸車？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T06:52:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b32e29c441be9bcb059eeabd7faf68e5b5920c5e","tid":666725,"uid":470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T06:53:59.000Z","msg":"已經係新款19座都仲要加多6個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"454b69e1bbb0fbba501e4332aaf7389082eb1b7b","tid":666725,"uid":13450,"like":2,"disli